description: Meridian Modern // Nestled between Seattle's downtown retail core and the vibrant Pike/Pine corridor, this freshly renovated home offers the perfect blend of urban convenience and luxury living. From the 25th floor of one of Seattle's most recognized towers, this rare 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence affords a level of spaciousness generally afforded ultra-exclusive penthouse homes. Offering unobstructed 270* views, the home has been fully re-envisioned with no detail overlooked—slate stacked stone tile, marble countertops, minimalist fir accents, Buster & Punch hardware, black stainless appliances, Sonos system, and roller shades—all contributing to a sleek, modern retreat. 2 parking, plus storage. 24h concierge. Exceptionally well-run HOA.
